<p><strong><span>（央视财经《天下财经》）</span></strong><span>商务部</span><span>11</span><span>日公布数据，</span><span>8</span><span>月份我国实际使用外资</span><span>841.3</span><span>亿元，同比增长</span><span>18.7%</span><span>，连续第</span><span>5</span><span>个月实现单月吸收外资金额增长。</span><span></span></p>
